{"tid":607078,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"中國再一次單方面將法律在香港實行?","createTime":"2018-03-27T03:48:32.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-30T15:32:50.000Z","uid":53416,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"5123287034fa1d1ed87fc4ae90cb15aeacc8d078","tid":607078,"uid":53416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-27T03:48:32.000Z","msg":"[url]<a href=\"http://m.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2377447\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2377447&d=%2BSS9QVwTI8hXb30NtyHLiosQCuff2cTRbXvS6e969MQ%3D&h=da92378a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2377447&h=3452592b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://m.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2377447</a><br />\n[/url]<br />\n<br />\n中國疑修例，不再向勸阻不聽還去危險國家的公民提供免費領事保護服務。聽落好似唔關你事？咁你就錯啦。<br />\n<br />\n咁出現問題啦，香港特别行政區護照持有人係由中國使領館提供領事保護，香港本身無提供，亦無權提供服務。<br />\n<br />\n香港政府本身亦無就外交部發出的外遊警告作出特別通報，香港本身就只有自己一套嘅外遊警示系統。香港居民唔會，亦無必要閱讀中國外交部的公告，相反外交部亦不會通報香港居民。<br />\n<br />\n再說，中國法律在香港沒有效力。但若果有關法例影響到香港居民在外的合法領事保護權，即等同中國單方面將法律在香港實行。<br />\n<br />\n咁就出現幾個問題啦。<br />\n<br />\n1. 有關法令會否影響香港特區護照持有人的領事保護權利?<br />\n2. 有關法例是否亦適於於香港特區護照持有人?<br />\n3. 當外交部與香港外遊警示系統出現不一致的情況下，香港人何去何從?<br />\n4. 你估個個外遊都係去玩嘅咩，因公出行的領事服務是否受到影響?<br />\n5. 最重要的是：這是否違反基本法的行為?<br />\n<br />\n個重點就係：若果有關法律在中國獲得通過的話，特區護照燒咗佢啦，用BNO好過。"},{"pid":"c5de3ac2e88bdaa7e86aeeca85ab2884d60c98b4","tid":607078,"uid":53416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-27T03:50:53.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://m.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2377447\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2377447&d=%2BSS9QVwTI8hXb30NtyHLiosQCuff2cTRbXvS6e969MQ%3D&h=da92378a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2377447&h=3452592b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://m.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2377447</a>"},{"pid":"6468e93d31cc2fc793c9afb75cd78ea714c77c3f","tid":607078,"uid":71323,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-27T04:12:01.000Z","msg":"佢本來就收完錢先考慮服唔服務㗎啦<br />\n而家只係講明咁解"},{"pid":"286253a9d10859bf99b7d9b480a503f83fd1ed0a","tid":607078,"uid":41245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-30T06:33:05.000Z","msg":"要討論㗎咩？<br />\n入得中國大使館就係佢地話事㗎啦<br />\n支那唔係法治國家<br />\n「修例」咪啫係佢地話事"},{"pid":"ac3d12cb23e348dd4e92daa1ff93c674be4f9d3f","tid":607078,"uid":33028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-30T06:42:02.000Z","msg":"佢個法例只係管海外中國公民，唔係所有香港居民，而且唔會適用於香港，點會等同中國單方面將法律在香港實行。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c020cf19361a9b8bb4e8cf4690fc9984b0d7eac","tid":607078,"uid":129739,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-30T06:43:08.000Z","msg":"用bno算"},{"pid":"2a6bc38f33757fbc8518bf1cb34c3283ad87d124","tid":607078,"uid":41245,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-30T06:48:50.000Z","msg":"一句講晒<br />\n拎特衰有事就要入支那大使館<br />\n話唔關事都on撚鳩"},{"pid":"58c3a6462181d38297b8554323535a8a8e141c19","tid":607078,"uid":92353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-30T07:03:13.000Z","msg":"其實無變<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 本身都唔存在嘅野 點樣取消變冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"04ff1f1ffc079b3bdeddcbea4f1fecbd5df8ad28","tid":607078,"uid":170665,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-30T14:10:45.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"42230e11a297e5ce23ab0f3201e0bf0edee846df","tid":607078,"uid":31841,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-30T14:11:40.000Z","msg":"關我撚事咩屌"},{"pid":"fcbe466a508f66d05a7e4db3ea193659b72ee7b2","tid":607078,"uid":49693,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2c020cf19361a9b8bb4e8cf4690fc9984b0d7eac",